Package BattleshipGame

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoatPosition
    BoatPosition gets variable for the rows and columns and return them when they are needed.
    ClientDriver
    ClientDriver generate the GUI of the client and run the game for the battleship
    ClientHandler
    ClientHandler generate the thread for the program and manage the transaction between clients and server.
    Controller
    Controller controls various status to manage the program.
    InputListener
    InputListener listens to the clients and server and read the objects, respond to observers.
    Message
    Message gets string value for the messages and stores them.
    Result
    Result gets string variable for the results of the clients turn.
    ServerDriver
    ServerDriver generate the GUI of the server and run the server for the battleship
